title: I'm in Love with the Villainess
subTitle: Rei Ohashi, an overworked employee, passes away after which she is reincarnated as Rae Taylor, her favourite video game's heroine, and gets attracted to Claire Francois, the main antagonist.

title: Blade Runner 2049
subTitle: K, an officer with the Los Angeles Police Department, unearths a secret that could create chaos. He goes in search of a former blade runner who has been missing for over three decades.

title: Baby Driver
subTitle: When talented getaway driver Baby meets his dream girl, Debora, he chooses to leave his shady life behind. But when he is called in for one last heist with an unstable crew, things get dicey.

title: Miss Bala
subTitle: Gloria gets abducted by a group of criminals when she visits Mexico to meet her friend Suzu. Later, she uses her wit to survive in the cruel world of crime.

title: Daddio
subTitle: A woman takes a cab ride back home from the airport. En route, she unexpectedly has an insightful conversation with the driver regarding the important relationships in life.

title: Insidious: The Last Key
subTitle: Parapsychologist Elise Rainier gets thrust into returning to her eerie childhood home where she and her family have to fight a dangerous otherworldly entity.

title: White House Down
subTitle: When terrorists suddenly invade the White House, police officer John Cale springs into action to protect his daughter and the President of the United States.
Jackson Curtis, a discontented writer, battles against all odds to keep his family secure when a series of apocalyptic calamities threaten to decimate humankind.

title: Anaconda
subTitle: A documentary crew, who are on a mission to find a tribe named Shirishamas, help a snake hunter when they find him stranded. However, he forces them to risk their lives and hunt down an anaconda.

title: Anacondas: The Hunt for the Blood Orchid
subTitle: A team of researchers is in Borneo to find the blood orchid, a flower that could hold the secret to eternal life. However, the scientists run afoul of the jungle's deadly snakes.

title: Anaconda 3: Offspring
subTitle: Peter Murdoch, a wealthy man, funds a project wherein two anacondas are tested in a research laboratory. Later, a mercenary is hired to stop the snakes after they escape and go on a killing spree.

title: Anacondas: Trail of Blood
subTitle: When an experiment goes wrong, a genetically enhanced anaconda offspring is unleashed. Possessing the power to regenerate, it quickly creates panic and destruction.

title: Brightburn
subTitle: Tori and Kyle find a baby boy in a spaceship and adopt him as their own child, Brandon. However, after turning 12, Brandon learns that he has superpowers and begins to use them for sinister purposes.

title: Men in Black: International
subTitle: Agent M, a probationary member of the MIB, teams up with Agent H and uncovers a sinister plot that reveals a traitor in the organisation aiding an alien invasion.

subTitle: In a future world ruined by war, robot dolls fight instead of people. A team of good robots battles evil robots that turned against humans.

subTitle: Abby, a lovelorn TV producer, finds herself in the midst of tests when she strikes a deal with her chauvinistic colleague, Mike, who wants to prove to her the accuracy of his relationship theories.

subTitle: Curtis and his family are asked to install an artificial intelligence program in their house in a bid to test it. However, they soon begin to experience disturbing occurrences.

subTitle: Count Dracula is overjoyed to witness the birth of his grandson, Dennis. However, when Dennis shows no signs of being a vampire, Dracula tries to help him unlock his powers.

title: Hotel Transylvania: Transformania
subTitle: When Van Helsing's invention goes awry, Johnny turns into a monster and Dracula becomes human. Later, they embark on a journey to find a cure before their transformations become permanent.

title: Sisu
subTitle: As WWII comes to an end, Aatami Korpi trudges towards retirement with a bag full of gold. However, when a Nazi soldier learns about the treasure, he chases after the warrior, unaware of his prowess.
